items.title: Kefka, Court Mage // Kefka, Ruler of Ruin (Borderless) (0322) [FINAL FANTASY]
items.body_html:
Set: FINAL FANTASY
Type: Legendary Creature — Human Wizard
Rarity: Mythic
Cost: {2}{U}{B}{R}
Whenever Kefka enters or attacks, each player discards a card. Then you draw a card for each card type among cards discarded this way.


8: Each opponent sacrifices a permanent of their choice. Transform Kefka. Activate only as a sorcery.
"Life.. Dreams... Hope... Where do they come from? And where do they go? Such meaningless things.. I'll destroy them all!"
Reverse Type: Legendary Creature — Avatar Wizard
Flying Whenever an opponent loses life during your turn, you draw that many cards.
